high_descs: Turn around and go straight back the room. Turn to the left at the counter.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Carry the spatula to the left and find the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the spatula.
Carry the spatula and go to the right, then turn right to find the microwave.
Place the spatula in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a spatula and place it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the counter by the recycling bin on the floor.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Turn left and walk forward to the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the side table containing the microwave.
Put the spatula on the table, in front of and to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned spatula on a side table.

high_descs: Turn around and start walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the end of the wooden counter.
Pick up the metal spatula off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the spatula into the sink basin then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the spatula.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the microwave.
Place the clean spatula on the counter in front and to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the counter.
